reviewText: This video was very poorly made. The photographs are extremely dark the zooming shots are very jumpy. The female narrator is uninspiring and does not have a pleasant voice. We are disappointed with this video. It seems to be an older quality video. We do not recommend the purchase of it.
The Grand Staircase Collection Covers Bryce, Zion, and the Grand Canyon. Awesome photography, good narration. Almost as good as being there!
